## 4. Development run scripts

### 4.1. Local Python environment

From repo root:

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

This uses the usual FastAPI + uvicorn pattern for local development. [fastapi.tiangolo](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/deployment/manually/)

### 4.2. Run the API

With `.venv` activated and `.env` present:

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
```

- API base: `http://localhost:8000`
- Docs: `http://localhost:8000/docs` (interactive Swagger) [fastapi.tiangolo](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/first-steps/)

Endpoints you should see in docs:
- `GET /internal/models`
- `GET /internal/quote`
- `GET /internal/ping`
- `POST /internal/execute`

